# Testing

- Unit tests live near modules; integration tests cross module seams per `integration-checkpoints.md` in Planning.
- E2E: PLD_PM uses Playwright + Firebase emulators; monorepo E2E to be added as features stabilize.
- CI must stay green before merging to `main`.
